('foundation', 'sentence-types', 'beginner', 'What is wrong? "What a beautiful flower."', '["Use: ! instead of period", "Add: !", "Remove: period", "All corrections needed"]', 0, 'Exclamatory needs !. Correct: "What a beautiful flower!" Exclamations must have exclamation mark not period.', 'medium'),

