('foundation', 'sentence-types', 'beginner', 'Choose: Express strong anger:', '["I am so angry!", "I am angry.", "Am I angry?", "Be angry."]', 0, 'Strong emotion = exclamation mark. "I am so angry!" = ! shows intensity. Pattern: Statement + ! (strong emotion).', 'medium'),

